---
title: Beef and Roasted Red Pepper Ragu with Spaghetti
description: This twist on classic spaghetti bolognese is packed with tender ground beef and tons of herby, garlicky flavour, all topped with a fresh sprinkling of Parmesan. It'll have everyone in your home going back for more!
